\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"575b83e00488f86df90a11bae3e00b93082fbc26","tid":1539770,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"599a3a2a21dde8def6c5c8d36514563f4e44cbb1","tid":1539770,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:22:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:24:10.000Z","msg":"你都岩喎，應該剩係得一粒<br />\n我諗住強調缺一不可嘛。。。"},{"pid":"78d04d1d25b316792dd6876e0dae30bc59566fdf","tid":1539770,"uid":283649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3eded61a1bef58277bc2f9f3fb5d5f671e10894","tid":1539770,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xMkXh97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxMkXh97.jpg&h=223e7470&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:24:29.000Z","msg":"係得一